## Runtime

{{KSTACK_RUNTIME}}

Use `$KSTACK_ROOT/browse/dist/browse` as the browse binary when you need an explicit path.
The browse server writes project-local state and logs under `.kstack/`.

## Rules

- Prefer `browse` for verification, repro, screenshots, and UI state checks.
- When a task changes the UI, update `.kstack/state` with a QA or design finding instead of leaving evidence only in chat.
- Save screenshots and ad hoc notes under `.kstack/reports/` when they matter for later review.

